Name: Faisal Abid
AboutMe:
Faisal is a Google Developer Expert, Entrepreneur and Engineer. He is a programming language enthusiast and loves solving software engineering challenges across the stack.

He is also a published author and has appeared in leading publications with articles in Node.js, Android, ColdFusion and Flex.

In his free time, Faisal leads Javascript, Node.js, Dart, or Android workshops and presents at conferences such as OSCON, JFokus, CodeMotion, and FITC.

During the days, you can find Faisal developing mobile applications either on iOS/Android, or writing backends in Dart or Node.js
